{"tid":2010612,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Tesla 不滿地方政府迫使工廠停工　入稟覆核並考慮遷離加州","createTime":"2020-05-10T13:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T14:02:41.000Z","uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fed4575293ed27d539271368ec06d14e197b254a","tid":2010612,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/105786681-1552323674808gettyimages-1128344984.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F105786681-1552323674808gettyimages-1128344984.jpeg&h=84a8e01b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><br />\n美國的疫情雖然稍爲受控，但是各地政府仍然實施各自的限聚令，其中 Tesla 方面雖然一直要求放寬讓他們可以繼續生產，但未有成功，因此最近就入稟法院覆核限聚令，並表示考慮遷離加州。<br />\n<br />\nTesla 總裁 Elon Musk 表示，他們已向加州的 Alameda 郡提起訴訟，認爲改郡的「臨時衛生官員」無知而且不由選舉任命，其推出的限聚令違反了州長、總統、美國憲法自由和簡單的常識。他指出 Tesla 擁有在中國工廠得到的經驗，對確保安全有充分了解，比這些低級代理官員更能掌握狀況。而且他們也在考慮將未來的業務撤離加州來抗議。<br />\n<br />\nAlameda 郡方面回應指，他們已經與 Tesla 方面密切合作制定安全相關計劃，希望讓他們的 Fremont 工廠復工至於能夠確保員工健康得到保障。Tesla 的 Fremont 工廠在 3 月 24 日開始停工，目前加州本身已經復工，但Alameda 郡仍然未解封，令 Elon Musk 相當不滿，曾經表示停工命令是法西斯主義。<br />\n<br />\n來源：CNBC</strong>"},{"pid":"6dc9ff68fd648bc0c3794a916ca8e69540534452","tid":2010612,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:54:21.000Z","msg":"商家佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bb821e6c620694edf45780cf6d83f143533c03","tid":2010612,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:56:01.000Z","msg":"去中國啦"},{"pid":"d85fe87b40822f6500d10689578aaf81317c2318","tid":2010612,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"將所有廠設晒喺中國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec24153c0c83207c3db90946c679abfdbcf02af6","tid":2010612,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"去支那囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾人偷技術偷晒啲錢囉"},{"pid":"8fb9ce3fd73acea99d387239016b449242632de3","tid":2010612,"uid":30145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:58:46.000Z","msg":"呢條賤種奶共但仲有唔少連登仔幫佢講說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡直第二個黃子華"},{"pid":"22f60ae9528f3d95205b0b09756db72432fd206b","tid":2010612,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:02:22.000Z","msg":"真心，係需要復工，唔係一味封城"},{"pid":"6cb52470fd516472b5564d85546d073d7c26b357","tid":2010612,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:02:41.000Z","msg":"呢鋪我撐musk"}]}